trans-unit.source: Specifies the default binding property for a component.
trans-unit.target: Angir standard binding-egenskapen for en komponent.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute is specified at the class level.
trans-unit.target: DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute er angitt på klasse-nivå.

trans-unit.source: It can be inherited and does not allow multiple attributes on the same class.
trans-unit.target: Det kan arves og tillater ikke flere attributter i samme klasse.

trans-unit.source: For more information about using attributes, see [Attributes](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan du bruker attributter [attributter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"></xref> class using no parameters.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av uten parametere.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A> property to `null`.
trans-unit.target: Standard konstruktør angir den <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A>egenskapen `null`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"></xref> class using the specified property name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av det angitte egenskapsnavnet.

trans-unit.source: This constructor sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A> property to the value of the `name` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren angir den <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A>egenskapen med verdien for den `name` parameteren.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the default binding property.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på en standard bindingen for egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: Represents the default value for the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Representerer standardverdien for den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The Default member is a static, read-only field that defines an instance of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute> class initialized with the default constructor.
trans-unit.target: Standardmedlemmet er et statisk, skrivebeskyttet felt som definerer en forekomst av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute>klassen er initialisert med Standardkonstruktøren.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified <xref:System.Object> is equal to the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den angitte <xref:System.Object>er lik gjeldende <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"> </xref> forekomsten.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: The Equals method returns `true` if the value of the `obj` parameter is of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute> and the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A> properties of the two objects are equal.
trans-unit.target: Metoden er lik returnerer `true` Hvis verdien for den `obj` parameteren er av typen <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute>og <xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A>Egenskaper for de to objektene er like.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute.Name%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Object> to compare with the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"></xref> instance
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Object>skal sammenlignes med gjeldende <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"> </xref> forekomsten</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the object is equal to the current instance; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, indicating they are not equal.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis objektet er lik gjeldende forekomst; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>, betyr det at de ikke er lik.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this instance.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer hashkoden for denne forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: A 32-bit signed integer hash code.
trans-unit.target: En 32-biters heltall med fortegn hash-kode.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the default binding property for the component to which the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"></xref> is bound.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på en standard bindingen for egenskapen for komponenten som den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"> </xref> er bundet.

trans-unit.source: The Name property is set in the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Name er angitt i konstruktøren.

trans-unit.source: The name of the default binding property for the component to which the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"></xref> is bound.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på en standard bindingen for egenskapen for komponenten som den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DefaultBindingPropertyAttribute"> </xref> er bundet.
